Description:
This Contract has already been awarded. This notice is for the publication of the Consultancy value Statement which indicates the financial and non-financial value which has been delivered from this Contract.

To undertake a strategic feasibility study, which takes account of the outputs of previous research, and to provide recommendations and indicative costs covering the following work strands;

The existing digital landscape for grants administration across government and its Arms Length Bodies;
The scope to introduce a new government grants data repository and interactive funding map; and
The scope to introduce a digital system that would enable, as far as is possible, the end-to-end grant administration process, for use by departments service and their Arms Length bodies (ALBs).
